(ABSTRACT) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Industrial machines rarely fail without warning signs. Sensor features such as air) Tj
T*
(temperature, process temperature, rotational speed, torque, and tool wear can shift before) Tj
T*
(breakdown. This project develops a supervised machine-learning workflow for early) Tj
T*
(machine-failure prediction using the AI4I 2020 predictive-maintenance dataset structure.) Tj
T*
(Five classifiers are trained and compared: Logistic Regression, K-Nearest Neighbors, Naive) Tj
T*
(Bayes, Decision Tree, and Support Vector Machine. Evaluation uses accuracy, precision,) Tj
T*
(recall, F1-score, ROC-AUC, confusion matrices, and ROC curves. Recall and F1-score are) Tj
ET
